The '''Horned Devil''', also known as the '''R.GOYLE''' or '''RED GARGOYLE'''<ref name="Enemy Identification Chart"/>, is an enemy in ''[[Final Fantasy]]''. It can be a dangerous enemy, as it is capable of attacking up to four times per round and casting a variety of magic, and always attacks in groups.

