== Behind the scenes ==
At one point in development, the Horned Devil's physical attacks may have been intended to inflict [[Poison (Final Fantasy status)|Poison]] or [[Stone (Final Fantasy status)|Stone]], as its attacks are flagged to check for resistance to the [[Poison (Final Fantasy element)|Poison]] element similar to enemies capable of inflicting those statuses, but no status is assigned to the Horned Devil. This quirk is present in all releases.

